import React from 'react' function MovieRec() { //userGenreList = props.userGenreList const userGenreList = ['romantic', 'adventure', 'sci-fi', 'suspense', 'anime'] const userMovieList = ['tt4566758'] let counter = 0 let omdbData let textToBeDisplayed = userGenreList[Math.round(Math.random() * userGenreList.length)] let url = "http://www.omdbapi.com/?apikey=[906b7c64]&i=" + userMovieList[counter].toString() fetch(url) .then(response => response.json()) .then(data => { omdbData = data }) console.log(url) return ( <>
{/*

{textToBeDisplayed}

*/}

{omdbData.Title.toString()}

Genre: {omdbData.Genre.toString()}

Director: {omdbData.Director.toString()}

{omdbData.Plot}

) } export default MovieRec
